"{    \"translations\": [        {            \"english_version\": \"The US president wants China and Taiwan to reduce tensions over the island. There were many ceremonies, but no trade deals were made after the two-day visit.\",            \"english_title\": \"US President on China-Taiwan Tensions\",            \"translated_version\": \"El presidente de Estados Unidos quiere que China y Taiw\u00e1n tengan menos problemas por la isla. Hubo muchas ceremonias, pero no se hicieron acuerdos comerciales despu\u00e9s de la visita de dos d\u00edas.\",            \"translated_title\": \"Presidente de EE.UU. sobre problemas China-Taiw\u00e1n\"        },        {            \"english_version\": \"A 66-year-old man turned himself in after an influencer used AI to pretend to be a 14-year-old girl and shared their conversation online.\",            \"english_title\": \"Man Surrenders After AI Prank\",            \"translated_version\": \"Un hombre de 66 a\u00f1os se entreg\u00f3 despu\u00e9s de que un influencer us\u00f3 inteligencia artificial para hacerse pasar por una ni\u00f1a de 14 a\u00f1os y comparti\u00f3 su conversaci\u00f3n en l\u00ednea.\",            \"translated_title\": \"Hombre se entrega tras broma de IA\"        },        {            \"english_version\": \"A New York jury is considering the case against a 74-year-old disgraced film producer for the third time.\",            \"english_title\": \"Jury Reviews Film Producer Case Again\",            \"translated_version\": \"Un jurado de Nueva York est\u00e1 considerando el caso contra un productor de cine de 74 a\u00f1os por tercera vez.\",            \"translated_title\": \"Jurado revisa caso de productor de cine otra vez\"        },        {            \"english_version\": \"The US president says Iran must show real commitment to stop using nuclear fuel and enriching uranium.\",            \"english_title\": \"US President on Iran's Nuclear Program\",            \"translated_version\": \"El presidente de Estados Unidos dice que Ir\u00e1n debe mostrar compromiso real para dejar de usar combustible nuclear y enriquecer uranio.\",            \"translated_title\": \"Presidente de EE.UU. sobre programa nuclear de Ir\u00e1n\"        },        {            \"english_version\": \"Israel's prime minister has ordered legal action over an article that claimed Israeli security officials raped Palestinian detainees.\",            \"english_title\": \"Israel PM Orders Legal Action\",            \"translated_version\": \"El primer ministro de Israel ha ordenado acciones legales por un art\u00edculo que dec\u00eda que oficiales de seguridad israel\u00edes violaron a detenidos palestinos.\",            \"translated_title\": \"Primer ministro de Israel ordena acci\u00f3n legal\"        }    ]}"